Content: I have a vstar 650 and this morning. I started it just like I always do and when it got warm I started to head to work. I got 4 miles from my house and the bike died and would not start again. I have installed new plugs within 4 months and this is the first time it has done this. Now it just turns over and over and will not fire up.
